Package ncl.team22.languagetutor.test

Class Summary
LevelSelectActivity Activity where the difficulty level for a test will be decided, test levels below the current user level will not be enabled
TestActivity Activity for handling test generation
TestData Class containing static methods and ArrayLists for LanguageEntity, for use in tests
TestResult Class containing static methods and integer value for keeping track of a test result as a user moves through test screens
TestReviewActivity Activity to allow user to view their final test score and review progress, methods to submit test and reset counter values will be called here
TestReviewGridActivity This activity represents the table of words to be reviewed
TopicsActivity Activity to allow selection of topics from database, show progress of user on specific tests and allow them to do a mixed test
